 and His Messenger, that Jesus is the servant of Allah and His Messenger, His word which He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35331,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/tawheed-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35318,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Glad tidings of Paradise for professing monotheism","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cO Abu Huraira, go forth and whomever you meet who testifies with conviction in his heart that there is no God but Allah, give him the glad tidings of Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 31\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/27\/essentials-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35318,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Essentials of salvation are pillars of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin\u00a0came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, show me a deed by which I may enter Paradise.\u201d The Prophet said,\u00a0\u201cWorship Allah and never associate anything with Him, establish the prescribed prayers, give the obligatory\u2026","rel":"","contex